  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个团队协作工具的流程图，核心是三个组件：Upware聊天室、Upware看板和Upware冲刺待办列表。我想先看看它们之间的消息流转关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "upware chatroom",
        "upware kanbanboard",
        "upware sprintbacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这三个是主要节点。我注意到您提到了两次\"Upware冲刺待办列表\"，是要分成两个实例吗？还是一个是Bail，另一个叫Code？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "upware sprintbacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，分成两个。Bail代表初始的待办池，Code是经过筛选后的执行待办。另外聊天室也拆两个：Audit是日常沟通，Define是任务定义环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "upware chatroom",
        "upware sprintbacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在把五个节点摆好：Audit和Define都是Groupware_ChatRoom类型，Bail和Code都是Groupware_SprintBacklog，Barg是Groupware_KanbanBoard。布局用从左到右。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "关系上，先看板和工作项的双向流动：Bail和Barg之间要互相箭头，表示待办和看板状态同步。然后Define要指向Barg，任务定义完进看板。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了：Bail到Barg，Barg回到Bail的双向，还有Define指向Barg。这样任务定义流入看板，看板和待办双向同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail -- Barg",
        "Barg -- Bail",
        "Define -- Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Code到Define也要连，执行过程中的问题回流到定义环节重新澄清。Audit到Define也要有，日常讨论沉淀为任务定义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Code指向Define，以及Audit指向Define。这样两条反馈回路都有了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code -- Define",
        "Audit -- Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要三个辅助节点：Place、Signal、Risk。Place要触发Press动作，Signal要指向Barg作为信号输入，Risk要指向Signal表示风险传导。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Signal",
        "Risk",
        "Press",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了Place到Press，Signal到Barg，还有Risk到Signal。这三个节点没有Groupware前缀，作为外部触发器存在。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place -- Press",
        "Signal -- Barg",
        "Risk -- Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "检查一下：Barg到Bail的回流是不是画反了？应该是Barg可以更新Bail的状态，方向没错。但Press那边，Place是触发器，Press是动作，这样写可以。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg -- Bail",
        "Place -- Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认完毕。最终结构：五个Groupware节点形成核心工作流，三个外部节点提供触发和信号输入。所有关系：Bail↔Barg双向同步，Define→Barg任务下发，Code→Define和Audit→Define双重反馈，Risk→Signal→Barg风险信号链，Place→Press独立触发。",
